query:
UPDATE melee
                    SET
                        emojicoin_0_locked = melee.emojicoin_0_locked + $2,
                        emojicoin_0_price = $3,
                        emojicoin_1_locked = melee.emojicoin_1_locked + $4,
                        emojicoin_1_price = $5,
                        volume = melee.volume + $6,
                        rewards_remaining = melee.rewards_remaining - $7
                    WHERE melee.melee_id = $1
